version_description:
New icon
Turn on Data Protection for all databases and key files stored in MiniKeePass
Skip "Backup" folder when searching
Fixed an issue where the password overlay stayed visible when resuming the app
Other minor bug fixes
Updated translat

Potential fix for files being deleted. It's a good idea to backup your password files regularly.

--1.5--
iOS 7 compatible
Integrated web browser with auto-type
Bug fixes

Fixed issue with '\' characters in auto-type fields
Updated translations
Fixed issues with PIN and TouchID
Fixed issue with the close database setting

MiniKeePass is being retired.

Follow instructions within the app to export your existing data.
